Objective is to create an application that captures the following things

Daily Ideas and thoughts

Dreams Goals and Aspirations

Daily to do's

Life goals

Work Goals

Educational goals

Side hustles

The application has Three Categories

Projects
  Tasks
  
To-Do's

Somedays

Archives

Reference

Once you imput your ideas thoughts and tasks into the app it does scheduling for you.

To start you schedule times when you are busy and times when you are not 

It uses geo location to remind you what to get when you are at a store or at home at work

When you put a task or project it gives you insites on how to do that and tips on how other people have succeeded in doing so

It asks you and estimated time you think the task or To-Do will take you and it automatically schedules you on your free time

it works well with any 
